<div class="main_content"><p><img src='/assets/images/header-images/Home/About-Us/Careers.jpg' alt='HM Cragg Work for Us'></p><h1>Work For HM Cragg</h1>

<p>When you join HM Cragg, you
become an owner of one of the most highly skilled and customer centric
companies in the power industry.&nbsp; HM
Cragg is a leader in offering power systems, power electronics, backup battery
applications, and other complementary products to business entities.&nbsp; As an employee and owner of HM Cragg, you
will represent the values of the company &ndash; honesty, trust, integrity, ethics,
and knowledge.&nbsp; This translates into a customer experience that&rsquo;s a &ldquo;WOW&rsquo;&nbsp;for
our clients - or we make it right.</p>
<p>We take this commitment from
our customer to our own people who manage and support this business.&nbsp; We offer an exceptional employment experience
starting with participation in our ESOP program and including a comprehensive
benefits package.&nbsp; We promote an
opportunity for challenge and growth along with progressive tools and
technology.&nbsp; If a dynamic and innovative
environment supports your interests, we encourage you to explore career
opportunities at HM Cragg.</p>
<p>We are growing and adding a
number of new and exciting positions to our team.&nbsp; Please visit the below link to find an
opportunity that best suits your career interests and needs.</p>
<h2>Job Search</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">To search for a particular career offered by HM Cragg, please<a href="http://hmcragg.prevueaps.com/jobs" target="_blank"> click
here.</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>

